title: El Yogurt Place
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant with a small retiail section selling health foods and supplements. Offers a house-made sunflower seed veggie burger, a vegetarian sandwich, mushroom burritos, and prickly-pear cactus (nopal) salad can be ordered vegan by omitting cheese. Vegans to specify no cheese.
streetAddress: Calle Cantera 360 Seccion Terrazas de Mendoza, Playas de Tijuana
